lex Castro / The Verge</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n  <p id=\"FILETq\">Well, it only took 15 years, but better late than never. </p>\n<p id=\"KjlLCR\">For the first time in its history, Uber ended the year having made more money than it spent on its ridehailing and delivery operations. <a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/uber-ceo-dara-khosrowshahi-helped-turn-billion-dollar-profit-2024-2\">As noted by <em>Business Insider</em></a>, the company <a href=\"https://investor.uber.com/news-events/news/press-release-details/2024/Uber-Announces-Results-for-Fourth-Quarter-and-Full-Year-2023/default.aspx\">reported an operating profit</a> of $1.1 billion in 2023, compared to a $1.8 billion <em>loss </em>in 2022. Moreover, Uber said it made a net inc", "page_rating_visits": 0, "artist": null, "tags": [], "dead": false, "age": null}, {"page_rating_votes": 0, "thumbnail": null, "bookmarked": false, "source": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "page_rating_contents": 0, "comments": [], "vote": 0, "permanent": false, "user": null, "source_obj__id": 61, "date_published": "2024-02-08T15:45:00+00:00", "language": "en", "link": "https://www.theverge.com/24065942/jbl-authentics-300-speaker-review-alexa-google-assistant", "title": "JBL Authentics 300 smart speaker review: two assistants at once", "album": "", "page_rating": 0, "description": "<p>JBL is the first to make Amazon Alexa and Google Assistant coexist on the same speaker, and it works quite well. But the price you pay for that convenience feels a little uneven.</p>\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/24065942/jbl-authentics-300-speaker-review-alexa-google-assistant\">Continue reading&hellip;</a>\n  </p>", "page_rating_visits": 0, "artist": null, "tags": [], "dead": false, "age": null}, {"page_rating_votes": 0, "thumbnail": null, "bookmarked": false, "source": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "page_rating_contents": 0, "comments": [], "vote": 0, "permanent": false, "user": null, "source_obj__i